name: Star Eater (Studio SyndiCat)
description:
Doctor O'Niel has gone rogue. She has created an army of space-eating machines that threaten the galaxy. You must find Doctor O'Niel and shut her facility down before it's too late! The safety of the galaxy is in your hands.

Star Eater is a retro-style, sci-fi FPS created as part of the 2021 Epic Mega Jam.
